  <bioghist id="aspace_a67ffa1104cca21e74f77fecbd0c03c0">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Charlie Ahearn (born 1951) is a New York City film director and creative artist. Although mainly involved in film and video production, he is also known as an author and radio host. He wrote, directed, and produced the 1983 hip-hop film "Wild Style."</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_8c0f60649139f4fd9ab14409e08bdc9d">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Collection includes film production records, flyers, posters, original art, videos, audio, oral histories, photographs, slides, and vinyl recordings documenting early hip hop culture and the film "Wild Style."</p>  </scopecontent>
